ce then dispatches a female police psychologist personally requested to talk him down from the ledge. However, things aren\'t as straightforward and clearcut as they appear to be. Written by Anonymous','As a police psychologist works to talk down an ex-con who is threatening to jump from a Manhattan hotel rooftop, the biggest diamond heist ever committed is in motion.','http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/M/MV5BMTc5MTE4MzY2N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjMwNDc3Ng@@._V1_SX214_.jpg','2012-01-27',6.6),(676,'Surviving Christmas',2004,'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0252028','tt0252028',NULL,5,'Drew Latham is an executive leading an empty, shallow life with only wealth on his side. Facing another lonely Christmas ahead, Drew wants to revisit his old childhood home and possibly relive some old holiday memories. But when he arrives, he finds that the house in which he was raised is no longer the home in which he grew up. Inhabited by another family, Drew offers a nice financial reward that has the family ringing. But is Drew\'s generous cash offer only the beginning of an annoying visitor who\'s a little too overeager to celebrate Christmas? Written by monkeykingma','A lonely, obnoxious young millionaire pays a family to spend Christmas with him.','http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/M/MV5BMTcwMTI4MTY3Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwOTUzMjcyMQ@@._V1_SY317_CR0,0,214,317_.jpg','2004-10-22',5.1),(677,'Forgetting Sarah Marshall',2008,'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0800039','tt0800039',NULL,5,'Peter is a composer and a likable sad sack who\'s devastated when his girlfriend of five years, Sarah Marshall, the star of a cheesy CSI-style crime show, dumps him. He weeps, he rails, he mopes. Finally, his step-brother Brian suggests Hawaii, so Peter heads for a resort on Oahu where, as he\'s checking in, he sees Sarah and her new beau, Aldous, a polymorphously perverse English rocker. The weeping and moping start again, until Peter is rescued by Rachel, a thoughtful hotel clerk who invites him to a luau and to hang out