ef reign in the Forbidden City, the object of worship by half a billion people; through his abdication, his decline and dissolute lifestyle; his exploitation by the invading Japanese, and finally to his obscure existence as just another peasant worker in the People\'s Republic. Written by Martin H. Booda <booda@datasync.com>','The story of the final Emperor of China.','http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/M/MV5BMTQyNDE4MDk4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjIyMjU1MQ@@._V1_SY317_CR4,0,214,317_.jpg','1987-10-23',7.8),(1128,'Weird Science',1985,'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0090305','tt0090305',NULL,5,'Two unpopular teenagers, Gary and Wyatt, fail at all attempts to be accepted by their peers. Their desperation to be liked leads them to \"create\" a woman via their computer. Their living and breathing creation is a gorgeous woman, Lisa, whose purpose is to boost their confidence level by putting them into situations which require Gary and Wyatt to act like men. On their road to becoming accepted, they encounter many hilarious obstacles, which gives the movie an overall sense of silliness. Written by Jeff Ranous <uslwsjgr@ibmmail.com>','Two nerdish boys attempt to create the perfect woman, but she turns out to be more than that.','http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/M/MV5BMTY3ODY2NzQ0M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzMxMTMyMQ@@._V1_SY317_CR8,0,214,317_.jpg','1985-08-02',6.5),(1129,'Killer Elite',2011,'http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1448755','tt1448755',NULL,5,'Based on a true story, Killer Elite pits two of the worlds\' most elite operatives - Danny, an ex-special ops agent (Jason Statham) and Hunter, his longtime mentor (Robert De Niro) - against the cunning leader of a secret military society (\'Clive Owen\'). Covering the globe from Australia to Paris, London and the Middle East, Danny and Hunter are plunged into a highly dangerous game of cat and mouse - where the predators become the prey. Written by Anonymous','When his mentor is taken captive, a retired member of Britain\'s Elite Special Air Service 